     numeric argument ARG, move back ARG pages.  This is the preferred
     way to go back in time.

`N' (Lynx-like keymap)
`n' (Info-like keymap)
     Move forward one page in history (`w3m-view-next-page').  Of
     course, this will work only if you've used `B' (`l' for the
